'''Aaron Reeder''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Wikyochee]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the under-sixteen years old category. He was eleven at the time his entry was published.<ref name="GalaxyMag 7">{{GalaxyCite|7|Design An Alien}}</ref>

